{"tid":1317889,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中學校長轟商場允警入內無理執法 危及平民 新城市否認","createTime":"2019-07-14T23:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T00:06:57.000Z","uid":68738,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"177e5ab00531651791a63b43154a3f7900f1e92c","tid":1317889,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T23:51:25.000Z","msg":"昨晚（14日）大批防暴警察在新城市廣場中庭追打市民，雖然新城市廣場兩度在網上澄清，未有報警求助以及帶領警察進入商場執行職務，但從網上片段可見，當防暴警察經過廣場的中庭時，2名懷疑是新城市廣場的職員，一直位於防暴警的前方，一同經過鏡頭前；防暴警察最終跟隨職員到商場另一方通道。浸信會呂明才中學校長溫家傑更在商場facebook留言，直斥場方「不知所謂」，容許警方進入商場內「無理執法」。<br />\n<br />\n溫向新城市廣場直斥，其10多歲的親戚步出戲院後，「喺你個場地俾警察圍；朋友90幾歲阿爸食完飯，嚇個半死。你哋新城市廣場點解可以容許警察入內，無理執法？簡直不知所謂。有搶劫嗎？有掉汽油彈嗎？有弄碎了玻璃嗎？都沒有。遊行人士要乘港鐵離開，（但又要他們）不經過新城市廣場，可以怎樣？」<br />\n<br />\n新城市廣場昨晚約10時於facebook表示：「對於網上有傳言指，新城市廣場報警，新城市廣場在此澄清並沒有報警，亦沒有求警協助。特此澄清。」不過，從網上流傳的片段可見，當防暴警進入商場時，兩名穿上制服、胸前有新鴻基標誌的人士，一直位於防暴警的前方，一同經過鏡頭前。片段最終見到，防暴警察跟隨該職員到商場另一方通道。<br />\n<br />\n至凌晨，新城市又再度在facebook表示：「新城市城廣場在此澄清，沒有報警，亦沒有同事帶警察在場內執行職務，同事只是在場內維持秩序，協助商場內的人士。由面向沙田大會堂的新城市廣場地面出入口，至3樓通往沙田港鐵站出入口的通道，均為24小時公共通道，必須開放予所有人士。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190715/59824360?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR203pzw1K2iBz0y8lquJx-ySVWK2ATIvES7TlXae0kj-2RnUzY30D8BA98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190715%2F59824360%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR203pzw1K2iBz0y8lquJx-ySVWK2ATIvES7TlXae0kj-2RnUzY30D8BA98&d=ljlrpVqLOnAgFN3Ei6%2BgJ80BU04RHr%2BP31d0xuhNw0M%3D&h=7099883d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190715%2F59824360%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR203pzw1K2iBz0y8lquJx-ySVWK2ATIvES7TlXae0kj-2RnUzY30D8BA98&h=a15344a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190715/59824360?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR203pzw1K2iBz0y8lquJx-ySVWK2ATIvES7TlXae0kj-2RnUzY30D8BA98</a>"},{"pid":"6292d1008f8071173061369b88bcd480b454ba09","tid":1317889,"uid":120715,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T23:56:30.000Z","msg":"班狗見你阻住唔俾入<br />\n可能隨時用胡椒噴霧射9你<br />\n重則打你一獲<br />\n話你阻狗辦工"},{"pid":"286dabc2fe490767d5783a3d2570f8aa4a6eccee","tid":1317889,"uid":28279,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T23:57:14.000Z","msg":"警察犯法，商場無能"},{"pid":"7418eaa12c7118dcd44ee8399851fbaac097ee2e","tid":1317889,"uid":172349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6292d1008f8071173061369b88bcd480b454ba09","tid":1317889,"uid":120715,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T23:56:30.000Z","msg":"班狗見你阻住唔俾入<br />\n可能隨時用胡椒噴霧射9你<br />\n重則打你一獲<br />\n話你阻狗辦工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T23:58:38.000Z","msg":"有射PP 員工？"},{"pid":"4fb0a12ab675998bd0cb6e780159951ebe123768","tid":1317889,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T23:58:44.000Z","msg":"文宣攻保皇：前線警中矢之的，偽建制派議員全部失蹤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316637\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316637</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"640253dc0501aa1c1e4c889a905bce47dde5e9a1","tid":1317889,"uid":120715,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7418eaa12c7118dcd44ee8399851fbaac097ee2e","tid":1317889,"uid":172349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6292d1008f8071173061369b88bcd480b454ba09","tid":1317889,"uid":120715,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T23:56:30.000Z","msg":"班狗見你阻住唔俾入<br />\n可能隨時用胡椒噴霧射9你<br />\n重則打你一獲<br />\n話你阻狗辦工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T23:58:38.000Z","msg":"有射PP 員工？"},"